title: Findel-Hawkins & Zuern Rally for @OspreyMTEN in Day Four of ITA Regionals
text: advanced to the semifinals of the doubles draw, winning their quarterfinals match 8-5. "It's always nice to get a win over a program with such rich tradition and success as Georgia," said coach . "Yannick and Jack played very well and stuck to their games better than I have seen all semester. We are looking forward to the challenge of Georgia Tech tomorrow."
